I have a digital capacitor meter I use, I found it pn line last year from China for $20, I don&#39;t remember the company. Do a google on capacitor meter. The mechanical caps usually have two sections for each band. I think one tunes the oscillator and the other the antenna. I have only gotten one conversion to work, and I just sold it. I tried two other radios this week and can&#39;t get either one to work with varactors. 

